{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/annabelle-creation-menyuguhkan-hal-hal-ngeri-sekaligus-bikin-gemas/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Annabelle: Creation, Menyuguhkan Hal-Hal Ngeri Sekaligus Bikin Gemas","content":"<p>Bagi penyuka film horor, Annabelle pasti menjadi salah satu dari list film yang wajib ditonton. Tiga tahun setelah kesuksesan film pertamanya, boneka ikonik ini kembali menebar teror lewat film keduanya berjudul Annabelle: Creation. Film ini merupakan prekuel dari film Annabelle<em> </em>pertama yang rilis tahun 2014.</p>\n<p>Berbeda dari film pertamanya, Annabelle: Creation dibesut oleh David F. Sanberg, sutradara yang sukses menggarap film Lights Out. Film pertamanya hanya mengantongi nilai 29% di laman Rotten Tomatoes. Sedangkan Annabelle: Creation menunjukkan penilaian yang lebih baik dari film terdahulu.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13899\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13899\" data-attachment-id=\"13899\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/annabelle-creation-menyuguhkan-hal-hal-ngeri-sekaligus-bikin-gemas/attachment/3-1-4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/3-1-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(www.rottentomatoes.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(www.rottentomatoes.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/3-1-4.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/3-1-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13899\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/3-1-4.jpg\" alt=\"(www.rottentomatoes.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13899\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(www.rottentomatoes.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Film dimulai dari kecelakaan tragis yang menimpa Bee (Samara Lee), putri semata wayang suami-istri yang berprofesi sebagai pembuat boneka bernama Samuel Mullins (Anthony LaPaglia) dan Esther Mullins (Miranda Otto). Dua belas tahun setelah kematian Bee, Samuel dan Esther mengundang seorang suster muda bernama Charlotte (Stephanie Sigman) dan enam gadis yatim piatu untuk tinggal di rumahnya. Dua di antaranya adalah Linda (Lulu Wilson) dan Janice (Talitha Bateman), gadis kecil yang kakinya cacat karena menderita polio.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13898\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13898\" data-attachment-id=\"13898\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/annabelle-creation-menyuguhkan-hal-hal-ngeri-sekaligus-bikin-gemas/attachment/1-124/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/1-19.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Janice dan Linda (cdn.traileraddict.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Janice dan Linda (cdn.traileraddict.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/1-19.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/1-19.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13898\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/1-19.jpg\" alt=\"Janice dan Linda (cdn.traileraddict.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13898\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Janice dan Linda (cdn.traileraddict.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Film ini terinspirasi dari kisah nyata sebuah boneka horor bernama Annabelle. Hingga kini boneka itu masih tersimpan di Museum Okultisme Lorraine Warren di Moodus, Connecticut. Tapi yang bikin merinding, kabarnya boneka ini masih suka bergerak sendiri bahkan menggeram sendiri pada pengunjung.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13903\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13903\" data-attachment-id=\"13903\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/annabelle-creation-menyuguhkan-hal-hal-ngeri-sekaligus-bikin-gemas/attachment/7-59/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/7-11.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Boneka Annabelle di Museum Okultisme Lorraine Warren, Moodus, Connecticut (i.dailymail.co.uk)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/7-11.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/7-11.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13903\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/7-11.jpg\" alt=\"Boneka Annabelle di Museum Okultisme Lorraine Warren, Moodus, Connecticut (i.dailymail.co.uk)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13903\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Boneka Annabelle di Museum Okultisme Lorraine Warren, Moodus, Connecticut (i.dailymail.co.uk)</p></div></p>\n<p>Mungkin ini hanya pendapat pribadi saya saja. Tapi ada beberapa hal bikin gemas dari film ini. Apa memang semua film horor di-setting begitu juga?</p>\n<p><strong>Sesuatu yang Dilarang Malah Bikin Penasaran</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13901\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13901\" data-attachment-id=\"13901\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/annabelle-creation-menyuguhkan-hal-hal-ngeri-sekaligus-bikin-gemas/attachment/5-97/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/5-15.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Annabelle: Creation &#8211; Official Trailer (Youtube)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Annabelle: Creation &#8211; Official Trailer (Youtube)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/5-15.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/5-15.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13901\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/5-15.jpg\" alt=\"Annabelle: Creation - Official Trailer (Youtube)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13901\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Annabelle: Creation &#8211; Official Trailer (Youtube)</p></div></p>\n<p>Seperti film horor kebanyakan, beberapa tokoh di Annabelle: Creation ini punya rasa penasaran yang sangat besar. Keingintahuan besar ini yang akhirnya menyeret ke situasi yang menyulitkan mereka sendiri. Rasa penasaran yang besar seringkali mengalahkan ketakutan. Setelah kena getahnya, tak jarang para tokoh ini masih saja mengulang perbuatan yang sama demi menjawab kecemasan yang masih berseliweran di benak.</p>\n<p><strong>Roh Jahat Menampakkan Diri Dalam Berbagai Wujud</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13900\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13900\" data-attachment-id=\"13900\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/annabelle-creation-menyuguhkan-hal-hal-ngeri-sekaligus-bikin-gemas/attachment/4-1-4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/4-1-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Annabelle: Creation &#8211; Official Trailer (Youtube)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Annabelle: Creation &#8211; Official Trailer (Youtube)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/4-1-4.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/4-1-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13900\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/4-1-4.jpg\" alt=\"Annabelle: Creation - Official Trailer (Youtube)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13900\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Annabelle: Creation &#8211; Official Trailer (Youtube)</p></div></p>\n<p>Kalau bro sis mengira ini kisah tentang roh dari anak pembuat boneka, kalian harus nonton dulu supaya tidak salah menyangka. Bila di Indonesia makhluk-makhluk halus menampakkan diri dalam wujud kuntilanak, pocong, tuyul, atau genderuwo, dunia barat punya wujud makhluk halus yang berbeda. Di film Annabelle: Creation ini saja, makhluk halus muncul dengan macam-macam bentuk. Melalui perantara boneka, memakai wujud gadis kecil, menyusup jadi orang-orangan sawah, hingga berwujud suster.</p>\n<p><strong>Tidak Semua Kejadian Bisa Dijelaskan Dengan Logika </strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13902\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13902\" data-attachment-id=\"13902\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/annabelle-creation-menyuguhkan-hal-hal-ngeri-sekaligus-bikin-gemas/attachment/6-76/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/6-14.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(media.winnipegfreepress.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(media.winnipegfreepress.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/6-14.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/6-14.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13902\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/6-14.jpg\" alt=\"(media.winnipegfreepress.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13902\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(media.winnipegfreepress.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Ada hal-hal di dunia ini yang tidak bisa dijelaskan dengan logika. Terkadang sesuatu yang terjadi itu tidak masuk akal. Beberapa orang tidak percaya, sebelum mengalaminya sendiri. Meski hal-hal gaib tidak dapat dibuktikan secara sains, nyatanya hal-hal demikian memang ada.</p>\n<p>Sudah cukup yakin untuk nonton filmnya? Atau butuh mengumpulkan keberanian lebih? Siapkan popcorn dan selimut untuk nonton di bioskop!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"bb252e08-f612-52a8-8b91-e70e75613df9"}}}